quotes.text: I don't want to do this!
Are you still touching me? (from Warcraft: Orcs & Humans)
Don't you have a kingdom to run?

You played the shareware, now buy the game. (in the shareware version)
In the retail version I'm much funnier. (in the shareware version)
8-player network and multiplayer capability with full Red Book audio and movies in the full retail version. Buy it now! (in the shareware version)
Even elder races get tired of waiting.
Don't force me to run you through! /
Don't force me to run you through! /
Tilt one back with me, dog!
Captain on the bridge. (from Star Trek)
You never touch the other elves like that.
Do that again and you'll pull back a stump!

Do you know who I am?
I'll fling a hammer at you!

Ach, there's no hope for this lad.

I would not do such things if I were you.
